'''拉邬语''' ([[外名与内名|内名]]：''{{IPA|la21 wu21}}'')<ref name="Yang2011"/>是一种在中国[[云南省|云南省]]玉溪市[[新平彝族傣族自治县|新平彝族傣族自治县]]水塘镇旧哈村<ref name="ynszxc">{{cite web|url=http://www.ynszxc.gov.cn/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=250326|website=ynszxc.gov.cn|title=新平县水塘镇旧哈村民委员会|access-date=2017-12-30|archive-date=2017-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171222052442/http://www.ynszxc.gov.cn/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=250326|dead-url=no}}</ref>由50名老年人使用的极濒危的未分类[[彝语|彝语]]。此外在云南省[[普洱市|普洱市]][[镇沅彝族哈尼族拉祜族自治县|镇沅彝族哈尼族拉祜族自治县]]九甲乡可能仍有人会说拉邬语。<ref name="Yang2011">[http://www.sil.org/iso639-3/cr_files/2012-067_lwu.pdf Yang (2011)] (ISO 639-3 documentation)</ref>拉邬语使用者目前被归为[[拉祜族|拉祜族]]，早些时候被归为[[彝族|彝族]]。

==分类==
Cathryn Yang(2012)<ref name="Yang2012">Yang, Cathryn. 2012. [http://journals.dartmouth.edu/cgi-bin/WebObjects/Journals.woa/1/xmlpage/1/article/410?htmlAlways=yes Phonology sketch and classification of Lawu, an undocumented Ngwi language of Yunnan] {{Wayback|url=http://journals.dartmouth.edu/cgi-bin/WebObjects/Journals.woa/1/xmlpage/1/article/410?htmlAlways=yes |date=20200530003040 }}. In ''Linguistic Discovery'', Volume 10, Issue 2, Year 2012. Hanover, NH: Dartmouth College. {{doi|10.1349/PS1.1537-0852.A.410}}</ref>认为拉邬语像是[[彝语中部方言|彝语中部方言]]，但注释道它不和拉祜语或傈僳语归在一类。

Andrew Hsiu(2017)<ref>Hsiu, Andrew. 2017. ''[https://zenodo.org/record/1249178/files/Lawu_languages.pdf The Lawu languages: footprints along the Red River valley corridor] {{Wayback|url=https://zenodo.org/record/1249178/files/Lawu_languages.pdf |date=20180518200659 }}''.</ref>认为拉邬语和在卢鹏&路伟(2011)中记录的云南省[[元阳县|元阳县]]大坪乡小坪子[[阿邬语|阿邬语]]<ref name="ynszxc2">{{cite web|url=http://www.ynszxc.gov.cn/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=197147|website=ynszxc.gov.cn|title=元阳县大坪乡大坪村委会小坪子村|access-date=2017-12-30|archive-date=2017-09-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170920172248/http://www.ynszxc.gov.cn/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=197147|dead-url=no}}</ref>有亲缘关系。<ref name="Lu2011">卢鹏; 路伟. 2011. 国际哈尼/阿卡区域文化调查: 中国元阳县大坪哈尼族阿邬人文化实录. Kunming: 云南人民出版社. {{ISBN|978-7-222-07999-1}}</ref>拉邬语和阿邬语形成了''[[拉邬语组|拉邬语组]]''。语言学证据支持阿邬人祖先从西北方来到[[红河|红河]]河谷，向下游迁徙到其现居地。

已经灭亡的[[乐舞语|乐舞语]]可能和拉邬语有亲缘关系，但具体地位因资料短缺不明确。

